 riÃªng Äáº¿n tá»« nhiá»u láº­p trÃ¬nh viÃªn khÃ´ng muá»n sá»­ dá»¥ng tÃ­nh nÄng nÃ y.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":44,\"width\":960,\"height\":480,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/wordpress_2.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-44\" width=\"960\" height=\"480\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>ThÃ nh tá»±u</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Cho Äáº¿n nay, cÃ¡ nhÃ¢n WordPress ÄÃ£ trá» thÃ nh má»t CMS phá» biáº¿n nháº¥t hÃ nh tinh vá»i cÃ¡c thÃ nh tá»±u sau:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>TrÃªn tháº¿ giá»i, cÃ³ khoáº£ng 25 bÃ i viáº¿t ÄÆ°á»£c ÄÄng lÃªn cÃ¡c website sá»­ dá»¥ng WordPress má»i giÃ¢y.</li><li>Sá» lÆ°á»£ng website lÃ m báº±ng WordPress chiáº¿m 27% tá»ng sá» lÆ°á»£ng website trÃªn tháº¿ giá»i.</li><li>Trong sá» 100% cÃ¡c website sá»­ dá»¥ng mÃ£ nguá»n CMS, WordPress chiáº¿m 60%.</li><li>PhiÃªn báº£n WordPress 4.0 Äáº¡t hÆ¡n 16 triá»u lÆ°á»£t táº£i chá» sau khoáº£ng hai thÃ¡ng.</li><li>WordPress ÄÃ£ ÄÆ°á»£c dá»ch sang 169 ngÃ´n ngá»¯ khÃ¡c nhau, bao gá»m phiÃªn báº£n Tiáº¿ng Viá»t ÄÆ°á»£c dá»ch Äáº§y Äá»§.</li><li>Chá» tÃ­nh cÃ¡c giao diá»n (hay cÃ²n gá»i lÃ  theme) miá»n phÃ­ trÃªn thÆ° viá»n WordPress.org thÃ¬ ÄÃ£ cÃ³ hÆ¡n 2.700 themes khÃ¡c nhau.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>TÃ­nh nÄng</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Dá» sá»­ dá»¥ng</li><li>cá»ng Äá»ng há» trá»£ ÄÃ´ng Äáº£o</li><li>nhiá»u gÃ³i giao diá»n cÃ³ sáºµn</li><li>Nhiá»u plugin há» trá»£</li><li>dá» phÃ¡t triá»n cho láº­p trÃ¬nh viÃªn</li><li>há» trá»£ nhiá»u ngÃ´n ngá»¯</li><li>cÃ³ thá» lÃ m nhiá»u loáº¡i website</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"right\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-right\"><strong>Thanh BÃ¹i</strong></p>\n