(99, 1, '2020-05-09 00:20:00', '2020-05-08 17:20:00', '<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>ÄÄng nháº­p vÃ o Google Classroom</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Truy cáº­p ÄÆ°á»ng dáº«n <a href=\"https://classroom.google.com\"><strong>https://classroom.google.com</strong></a> vÃ  chá»n <strong>Go to Classroom</strong>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":156,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/ggclassroom_1-1024x486.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-156\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>ÄÄng nháº­p vÃ o báº±ng tÃ i khoáº£n Google</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":157,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/ggclassroom_2.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-157\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>NgoÃ i ra náº¿u báº¡n ÄÃ£ ÄÄng nháº­p sáºµn vÃ o Google thÃ¬ khi truy cáº­p trang web sáº½ hiá»n ra báº£ng xÃ¡c nháº­n tham gia Google Classroom.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>ÄÄng nháº­p thÃ nh cÃ´ng sáº½ hiá»n ra giao diá»n nhÆ° hÃ¬nh.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":158,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/ggclassroom_3-1024x420.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-158\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":159,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/ggclassroom_4-1024x255.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-159\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n