(178, 1, '2020-05-31 00:39:08', '2020-05-30 17:39:08', '<!-- wp:image {\"id\":44,\"width\":950,\"height\":475,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/wordpress_2.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-44\" width=\"950\" height=\"475\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<p>á» pháº§n nÃ y mÃ¬nh sáº½ hÆ°á»ng dáº«n cÃ¡c báº¡n cÃ i Äáº·t cÆ¡ báº£n WordPress. Báº¡n nÃ o chÆ°a tÃ¬m hiá»u WordPress thÃ¬ cÃ³ thá» xem bÃ i viáº¿t <a href=\"http://localhost/wordpress/2020/05/03/gioi-thieu-wordpress/\"><strong>Giá»i thiá»u WordPress</strong></a>. BÃ¢y giá» mÃ¬nh sáº½ báº¯t Äáº§u.</p>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>CÃ¡c báº¡n tiáº¿n hÃ nh download srouce code WordPress trÃªn trang wordpress.org. Giáº£i nÃ©n ra ÄÆ°á»£c folder âworpressâ lÃ  nÆ¡i chá»©a source code. Sau ÄÃ³ tiáº¿n hÃ nh truy cáº­p vÃ o Äá» cÃ i Äáº·t. á» ÄÃ¢y mÃ¬nh sá»­ dá»¥ng wampp Äá» táº¡o mÃ¡y chá»§ localhost.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":60,\"width\":747,\"height\":493,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/wordpress_3.png\" alt=\"source-code-wordpress-sau-giai-nen\" class=\"wp-image-60\" width=\"747\" height=\"493\"/><figcaption>Source code cá»§a WordPress sau khi giáº£i nÃ©n</figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Táº¡o database:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>CÃ¡c báº¡n truy cáº­p vÃ o phpmyadmin thÃ´ng qua ÄÆ°á»ng dáº«n <strong>localhost/phpmyadmin</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sau ÄÃ³ ÄÄng nháº­p vÃ o database mySQL. MÃ¬nh dÃ¹ng tÃ i khoáº£n máº·c Äá»nh vá»i username lÃ  ârootâ vÃ  máº­t kháº©u Äá» trá»ng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align